⍝ Laminate.tc
⍝ ═══════════

      ⎕IO←1

      ⍝ Precond: X fractional scalar between axes; implicit ⎕IO
      ⍝ inv: ⍴⍴Z ←→ 1+(⍴⍴A)⌈⍴⍴B
      A ← ⎕RVAL 2 (3 4) (,0 1 0 0 0)
      B ← ⎕RVAL 2 (3 4) (,0 1 0 0 0)
      Z ← A,[0.5]B
      (⍴⍴Z) ≡ 1+(⍴⍴A)⌈⍴⍴B
1
      ⍝ inv: ⍴Z ←→ (2,⍴A)[⍋0.5,⍳⍴⍴A]   for A=B same shape
      (⍴Z) ≡ (2,⍴A)[⍋0.5,⍳⍴⍴A]
1
